Implements the external drag&drop emulation.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "word"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("OnDropEvent", [{
  "type": "onbeforedrop",
  "x" : pos.x,
  "y" : pos.y
}]);

window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("OnDropEvent", [{
  "type": "ondrop",
  "x" : pos.x,
  "y" : pos.y,
  "text" : "test text",
  "html" : "<span>test html</span>"
}]);
```

params.description:
The drag&drop event type:
<b>onbeforedrop</b> - an event that is fired when the selected text or element is dragged;
<b>ondrop</b> - an event that is fired when the selected text or element is dropped on a valid drop target.

examples:
